@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_xkvffh(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.exp(wp.sin(wp.abs(v1 + 0.61)))
    tmp = wp.sin(wp.exp((v0 + 0.59 + tmp + 0.85)))
    v1 = wp.cos(v0)
    v2 = (wp.sin(wp.abs(tmp + 0.93)) / ((v1 + 0.74 - v1 + 0.27) + wp.sin(v2 + 0.55)))
    data[tid] = v0
